### Pagination & Filtering: Drill 4

### 1. Default pagination (Page 1, Limit 5)
GET http://localhost:3003/tasks

### 2. Specific pagination (Page 2, Limit 10)
GET http://localhost:3003/tasks?page=2&limit=10

### 3. Filtering by completed status
GET http://localhost:3003/tasks?completed=true

### 4. Sorting options
GET http://localhost:3003/tasks?sort=title&order=asc

### 5. Combined: Page 3, Limit 5, completed=false, sort=createdAt, order=desc
GET http://localhost:3003/tasks?page=3&limit=5&completed=false&sort=createdAt&order=desc

### 6. Invalid query param (validation error)
GET http://localhost:3003/tasks?limit=abc
